code: @Override public IntType getRandom(Random rnd) {     return new IntType(rnd.nextInt()). }
@Override public void write(DataOutputView out) throws IOException {     out.writeInt(this.value). }
@Override public void read(DataInputView in) throws IOException {     this.value = in.readInt(). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj instanceof IntType) {         IntType other = (IntType) obj.         return this.value == other.value.     } else {         return false.     } }
